{"tid":561113,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚有青光眼","createTime":"2018-02-14T17:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T00:05:12.000Z","uid":47485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"abcaae05a98b9fc9852ae85111b471affa2167ab","tid":561113,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"我一年前已經單耳突然聽唔到野（已開過post)<br />\n醫生醫過只醫到低音聽得到<br />\n<br />\n醫完耳之後發現眼睛睇唔清野<br />\n睇眼科發現眼壓高 大約24度<br />\n最近一次個幾月前去覆診<br />\n話再高左一度 25度<br />\n最近幾日發現頭痛同眼痛<br />\n我好擔心 青光眼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通個天又要我突然聽唔到仲要我突然睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近仲要過年<br />\n我預約眼科要等到26號先有得睇呀 點算"},{"pid":"dc4cc71e48c35acefc48247516db03d7d198f836","tid":561113,"uid":58928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過入急症？"},{"pid":"a9b1abd2fa87cf1caafd1fddb3f6768398a40f6d","tid":561113,"uid":93610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"隻眼係唔係每逢訓醒好似比人打一拳咁痛法？"},{"pid":"845ddead2931a1fae99e6e4279437e25a51c0c54","tid":561113,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc4cc71e48c35acefc48247516db03d7d198f836","tid":561113,"uid":58928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過入急症？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"上年聾果時頭暈到作嘔<br />\nCall白車入急症<br />\n個黃綠醫生 check 兩check 就比止暈藥叫我走<br />\n等左成十日先有得睇專科"},{"pid":"d5db19afb1ac4b61164a846aa1777abdd8073324","tid":561113,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845ddead2931a1fae99e6e4279437e25a51c0c54","tid":561113,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc4cc71e48c35acefc48247516db03d7d198f836","tid":561113,"uid":58928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過入急症？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"上年聾果時頭暈到作嘔